name: Block
title: Block
description: Block number

name: BlockCol
title: BlockCol
description: Column number within block

name: BlockRow
title: BlockRow
description: Row number within block

name: Col
title: Col
description: Column number

name: Combo
title: Combo
description: Identifies the Lentil-Wheat combination evaluated in this plot.

name: Comment
title: Comment
description: General comments from the field crew that may be pertinent to know during analysis.

name: Days_to_Emergence
title: Days to Emergence (date)
description: The number of days from the date of planting to the \"Emergence Date\".

name: Emergence_Date
title: Emergence Date (date)
description: The date on which at least 50% of the seeds within the plot are visible above the soil.

name: Expt
title: Expt
description: Captures the particular siteyear and Lentil/Wheat portion of the experiment evaluated in this row. This also indicates where and then these data were collected.

name: Flowering_Date_R1
title: Flowering Date (R1; date)
description: The date at which there is one open flower at any node on 50% of the plants in the plot. This is R1 in the Lentil Reproductive & Maturity Staging Guide.

name: Half_Pods_Mature_R7
title: Days till 10% of Plants have 1/2 Pods Mature (R7; days)
description: The number of days from the date of planting to the \"Maturity Date\" where the Maturity date is the date the plants reach R7 according to the Lentil Reproductive & Maturity Staging Guide.

name: Lentil
title: Lentil
description: Uniquely identifies the Lentil germplasm planted in this plot within the trial.

name: Lodging
title: Lodging (scale; 1=upright; 5=prostrate)
description: Indicates the rate of lodging in the plot between R6-R7 where lodging is defined as an irreversible falling over of the primary plant stem greater than 45 degrees.

name: Maturity_Date_R7
title: Maturity Date (R7; date)
description: This is R7 in the Lentil Reproductive & Maturity Staging Guide.

name: NIR
title: NIR
description: Protein percentage estimated by Near Infrared Spectroscopy (updated calibration)

name: NIR_LenPro_preTweak
title: NIR_LenPro_preTweak
description: Protein percentage estimated by Near Infrared Spectroscopy (old calibration)

name: Name
title: Name
description: The full name of the Lentil or Wheat germplasm evaluated in this particular row.

name: One_Open_Flower_R1
title: Days till 10% of Plants have One Open Flower (R1; days)
description: The number of days from the date of planting to the \"Flowering Date\" where the Flowering date is the date the plants reach R1 according to the Lentil Reproductive & Maturity Staging Guide.

name: Planting_Date
title: Planting Date (date)
description: The date the seeds were sown.

name: Rep
title: Rep
description: Replication number

name: Row
title: Row
description: Row number

name: Type
title: Type
description: Treatment or check

name: UniqueID
title: Unique ID
description: Uniquely identifies the particular plot within the larger trial. It consists of the year the plot was grown, the Plot ID and either the Lentil OR Wheat ID depending on which is grown when these data are taken.

name: Wheat
title: Wheat
description: Uniquely identifies the Wheat germplasm planted in this plot within the trial.

name: plot
title: Plot

name: yield_plot
title: yield plot (g)
description: The weight of the seed harvested from the plot by the combine.

name: yield_subsample

name: yield_total

description: For subsampled plots this is the yield from both the combine and the subsample. For others this will be equal to the plot yield measurement.
